defaultThe thinking extolled in this book has formed the basis of the visionary opinions promoted by the Ellen Mac
defaultA
defaultrthur 
defaultF
defaultoundation and other leading experts. 
default 
defaultThe book explains how natural systems in the Earth’s environment allow a circular flow of materials in, for example, the growth cycles of a tree. 
default 
defaultSince mankind learned how to extract and refine materials describe
defaultd as ‘technical nutrients’ (for example,
default steel, glass, plastic) another parallel,
default 
